In the INTEREST OF K.C., Minor Child, B.L., Mother, Petitioner-Appellant, T.L., Father, Respondent-Appellee. No. 18-1022 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed December 5, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

A mother appeals the district court's decision denying her petition seeking to terminate the father's parental rights. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
